The curing process takes just minutes, and your nails won't chip or peel for 2-3week. How to use UV-Nails gel polish? Step 1. Push the cuticles back and buff the nail to avoid smooth surface. (must file the edge of each nail). Clean the dust with DRY towel only Step 2. Apply a Thinlayer of the base coat. Step 3.Dry for 30-45 seconds under LED lamp or two minutes under the UV. Step 4. Apply a Thin layer of the UV-Nails gel polish color and dry for 30-45 seconds under LED lamp or two minutes under the UV light. Step 5.If the color is not showing well, please apply one more THIN layer and dry for 30-45 seconds under LED lamp or two minutes under the UV light. Step 6. Apply a thin layer of the top coat and dry for 30-45 seconds under LED lamp or two minutes under the UV light. Step 7. Take your hands out of the lamp and wait 10 seconds. Step 8. Use cotton ball and rubbing alcohol to remove the sticky layer from the nail. Step 9. Apply the cuticle oil and let it dry. Step 10. Done. How often do I need to use UV-Nails? You can use the system as often as you'd like. Usually, once you go through the nail curing process, nails don't chip or peel for 2-3 weeks. The beauty of the system lies in the fact that you can change your nail color at any moment and enjoy salon quality nails.

Title: Cosderma Glycolic Peel 35%(50 ml)
Description: Glycolic Peel 35% Gel Peel Treats Acne, Scars, Sun Damage And Fine Lines.Glycolic Acid Works As An Exfoliating Agent Because Of Its High Acidity But Easy Solubility. When Placed On The Skin As Part Of An Exfoliating Cream Or Gel, Glycolic Acid Goes Under The Damaged Upper Layers Of Skin And Destroys The ‘Glue’, Which Holds Dead Skin To The Surface. As This Dead Skin Is Chemically Burned Off, The Other Ingredients Carry The Individual Flakes Away And A Water Rinse Neutralizes The Remaining Acid. The Result Is A Much-Smoother Skin Surface And A More Youthful Appearance. Title: Adore Henna Natural Mehendi

Cover your hair with shower cap and leave it for 30 min. (*It may require 50-60 min., depend on hair condition).4. Rinse off the paste thoroughly.Note :- Apply a small quantity of the hair dye as prepared for use to the area and allow it to dry. After 24 hours wash the area gently with soap and water.
